      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        On 14th August 2025, a sudden and severe cloudburst struck the region of Chositi in Kishtwar district,
        Jammu & Kashmir, triggering catastrophic flash floods. The overwhelming surge of water and debris
        swept through villages, causing extensive destruction to homes, infrastructure, and agricultural land.
      </p>
