    <section>
      <h2>Impact</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Over 65 people lost their lives in the flash flood.</li>
        <li>Hundreds of residents were injured, many critically.</li>
        <li>Numerous people are reported missing, with ongoing rescue efforts.</li>
        <li>More than 1,200 homes were damaged or destroyed.</li>
        <li>Key roadways and communication lines were severely disrupted.</li>
        <li>Local agriculture suffered heavy losses due to flooding and landslides.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
